      <p class="supporting-questions">Antiperspirants contain aluminum compounds that temporarily block sweat glands to reduce sweating. Deodorants (like Lume) mask or neutralize odor without affecting sweat production. Aluminum-free deodorants like Lume are preferred by people concerned about aluminum exposure or who want to allow natural sweating while controlling odor.</p>
